msgid "This locker has no keyhole."
msgstr "這個儲物櫃沒有鑰匙孔。"

msgid "They're already open, so there's nothing to cut."
msgstr "它們已經被打開了，所以沒有東西需要被割開。"

msgid "Boxes filled to the brim with cleaning products."
msgstr "裝滿了清潔用品的箱子。"

msgid "It's packed with white chalk and nothing else."
msgstr "除了白粉筆外沒有其他東西了。"

msgid "This must be like... a year's supply."
msgstr "看起來是...一年份的使用量。"

msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "They're packed too tightly, I can't pull any out."
msgstr "裝得太緊了，我沒辦法拔出來。"

msgid "Some boxes filled with left shoes and lighters."
msgstr "裝著左邊鞋子和打火機的箱子。"

msgid "Some brand new brooms."
msgstr "一些全新的掃帚。"

msgid "A calendar... probably."
msgstr "日曆...大概吧。"

msgid "There are no dates or month names in it."
msgstr "上面沒有日期或是月份。"

msgid "A cleaning cart."
msgstr "清潔推車。"

msgid "It's sparkling clean."
msgstr "看起來閃閃發亮。"

msgid "A lamp. There's no light bulb nor a slot to place one."
msgstr "立燈。沒有燈泡或是可以放燈泡的插槽。"

msgid "A large locker. It's sealed shut."
msgstr "大儲物櫃。被關得很緊。"

msgid "A trash can. You can't see the bottom."
msgstr "垃圾桶。妳沒辦法看到它的底部。"

msgid "That's... weird."
msgstr "這還真...奇怪。"

msgid "What is?"
msgstr "哪方面？"

msgid "The existence of this room... makes no sense."
msgstr "這個房間的存在...沒有道理。"

msgid "What do you mean?"
msgstr "什麼意思？"

msgid "Based on the shape of the school, there can't be a room here. It would be floating in the air when seen from outside."
msgstr "依據學校的格局，這裡不該有房間。否則這間房間會飄浮在空中。"

msgid "Interesting..."
msgstr "有趣..."

msgid "But... we didn't even finish the ritual! What's happening?"
msgstr "可是...我們連儀式都沒有完成！現在是什麼狀況？"

msgid "I don't know..."
msgstr "我不知道..."

msgid "Isn't it exciting!?"
msgstr "這不是很令人興奮嗎！？"

msgid "Let's keep going."
msgstr "我們走下去吧。"
